# Business Rules

Implement:

- One finalized invoice per completed order.
- Cancelled invoices require authorization.
- Credit Note amount cannot exceed invoice amount.
- Debit Note must reference an existing invoice.
- Tax values cannot be negative.
- Invoice totals must equal line totals.
- Invoice numbers must be unique per Tenant.
- Prevent editing finalized invoices.

